{"tid":1128842,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺喺香港要成功要掌握 2 個 abilities","createTime":"2019-04-28T06:00:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T01:29:10.000Z","uid":125976,"like":22,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f817093209a4168b821735d6e5d549004fa12090","tid":1128842,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T06:00:46.000Z","msg":"1. Blowaterability (吹水能力)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. Capwaterability (搵水魚能力)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Showcases</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>A. 做 IT 狗</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>High Blowaterability</strong><br />\n做 IT Consultant，鳩吹吓月入過十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>High Capwaterability</strong><br />\n識得搵好工，喺適當時後跳槽，跳一次加幾千，玩幾年四五皮一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Loser</strong><br />\n揀親都伏工，又唔識跳，苦心揼足十年，就算技術幾勁都係得兩三皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>B. 做投行狗</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>High Blowaterability</strong><br />\n吹水叻，Sell 鳩啲 client 買貴基金，月入過十萬。做兩年 quit，之後呃政府創投基金，請 IT 狗整件垃圾再 sell，又賺一筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>High Capwaterability</strong><br />\n操盤叻，係咁開啲釣魚盤引班散戶買，再用期權殺到對家仆街冚家剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Loser</strong><br />\n苦心幫好多人搞 IPO，日日捱通宵砌靚啲數，但到最後只係公司一名卒仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe58e53d1538168b2729d3011b7b48d5d8eb0be","tid":1128842,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T08:48:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"673a8f69cc8d38fd25bce8cb778b13a3de0b5950","tid":1128842,"uid":115510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T08:49:39.000Z","msg":"敦倫金"},{"pid":"387029fdf7a2d3b31674ad0bcbb0a5b44e7d9d7d","tid":1128842,"uid":108022,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T08:54:14.000Z","msg":"要成功要掌握 2 個 abilities: 父幹, 西幹<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9729c090fe12da89fbc8362c211e4a3e6aecbb12","tid":1128842,"uid":249885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T09:06:31.000Z","msg":"巴打有無睇過個政府工巴打驚自己無料嘅po 根本愈無料愈上位 外行人管內行人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b22223013b9ed58b258319d578335b1bde489e1b","tid":1128842,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T09:07:30.000Z","msg":"巴打都係唔好做IT 狗 吹下水呃鳩人咪算 點解要咁辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俾誠哥玩值得咩"},{"pid":"a3f4909cdf4fddc4a8397138d40ef9d2be87c605","tid":1128842,"uid":107686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T11:01:56.000Z","msg":"聽君一席話 勝讀BBA"},{"pid":"3bddf6d0a8